Comprehensive API/protocol alignment with Discord conventions.

Closes #214, #215, #216, #217, #218, #199, #198

### Changes
- Fix opcode 4 collision (#214)
- Add ownership checks on mutations (#215)
- Standardize error format (#216)
- Fix channel-delete response + bulk-delete (#217)
- Add GET /gateway/bot (#218)
- Dispatch CHANNEL_CREATE/DELETE events (#199)
- Add last_message_id to channels (#198)
